      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-def-num-prt          .
           move      zero                 to   w-def-num-prc          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open moduli accettazione                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   opn-mdl-acc-000      thru opn-mdl-acc-999        .
       pre-exe-pgm-999.
