       acc-num-prt-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-num-prt-025.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio valore pre-impostazione         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-num-prt        to   w-sav-num-prt          .
       acc-num-prt-050.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
