      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-num-prc        not  = zero
                     go to acc-num-prc-100.
           move      w-det-ult-prc-att    to   w-tes-num-prc          .
       acc-num-prc-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
