      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-num-prt        to   w-fnd-arc-osk-prt      .
           perform   fnd-arc-osk-000      thru fnd-arc-osk-999        .
           if        w-fnd-arc-osk-sel    not  = spaces
