      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                not  = "DO  "
                     go to acc-qta-ass-999.
           perform   cnt-tdo-nok-000      thru cnt-tdo-nok-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg    =    spaces
                     move  "S"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-tes
                     go to acc-qta-ass-999.
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg      .
           go to     acc-qta-ass-100.
       acc-qta-ass-999.
           exit.

